node.text:
We wanted the summer house to have a bright, clean coastal feel without over doing it. Elegance with a touch of coastal warmth. The shelves from @jkhomefurnishings add a perfect metallic touch for that desired modern & elegant style. To see more of my home follow my personal page @graceslovefordesigns
.
All links are listed here: 

Chandelier by @hudsonvalleylighting

node.text:
First I styled my gorgeous new dresser from @jkhomefurnishings. Then I added a touch of a cozy Autumn palette 🍁 to the rest of the room.  Try it yourself! 1. Warm up with throw blankets 2. Candles to set the mood 3. Pillows that feature earthy colors and complement your autumn decor. (Dresser Link in stories) To see more of my home follow @graceslovefordesigns. Art by Luxeartdesigns.com
.
